  "description": "GloomCraft is a two dimensional top down roguelike/roguelite which uses hard shadows as an advantage against the player to hide enemies or important elements. The player plays as a mage that can brew potions and upgrade weapons with different alchemical resources gathered from the dungeon.\n\nControls:\n- WASD or Arrow Keys to Move\n- 'Z' Key to Show or Hide Inventory\n- Left Shift, Right Shift, or Space to Roll\n- 'Q' to Interact with Stairs\n- 'E' to Interact with Treasure Chests, Shop Stands, or Crafting Benches\n- Mouse to Aim, Left Click to Shoot, Right Click to Throw Away Potion/Flask\n- Click on Slots of Digit Keys to Select Equipment\n\nThis game has been made in 14 days for the Pirate Software Game Jam #15. All of the assets used in this game (sprites, images, sounds, music, font, code) has been made by me. Most of those have been made within the two-week timeframe.\n\nLink to my Submission: https://itch.io/jam/pirate/rate/2856425\nLink to the Game Jam: https://itch.io/jam/pirate\n\nSprites made using Pixilart\nFont made using PixelForge\nMusic made using UltraBox (BeepBox Mod)\nSounds generated using JSFXR"
}